[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] Whether you’re a total beginner or an experienced developer, **this learning process may still be hard**.
[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] Over time, we become used to certain things, and it can be painful to change.
[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] **But without change, there is no challenge** and without challenge, there is no growth.
[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] In this guide we’ll set up our first Hanami project and build a simple web app.
