[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] Hanami is a Ruby framework designed to create software that is well-architected, maintainable and a pleasure to work on.
[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] These guides aim to introduce you to the Hanami framework and demonstrate how its components fit together to produce a coherent app.
[src:hanami-ruby/getting-started] Ideally, you already have some familiarity with web apps and the Ruby language.
